  "description": {
    "zh": "现在大伙都知道，你现在似乎在很多人中间都很有名，有好评也有差评。在这一行中，总是结交朋友的同时也树立敌人，但这就是规则。\n\n最近，我的一个朋友联系了我，他对你这种人有多可信很感兴趣。嗯，能证明什么的只有看你自己，如果你还有任何未完成的事儿，我建议你先完成它们。\n\n我派团队去商场时，我手下的一个人带回来了一些书，其中一些可能会帮助你提升技能，甚至教会你如何制作一些新东西。加油吧，让它们变成属于你的东西。",
    "en": "Word got around, you seem to be known among a lot of people now, both positive and negative. Always making friends aswell as enemies along the way, that's how it works.\n\nA friend of mine contacted me very recently and got curious on how trustworthy someone like you can be. Well, the only one who can prove anything here is you, if you still have any open contracts I suggest you finish those.\n\nOne of my guys took some books with him when I sent a team out to the mall, some of them might be able to help you improve certain skills or even teach you some new ones. Get to work and they shall be yours."
  },
